long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Look, save, consolidate.

Visual bookmarking and note taking app_
   _for researchers, self-learners, designers and everybody else.

You have tables,
you can save images, videos, texts from the internet,
you can take notes,
you can create #hashtags and filter,
you are free to resize any content,
enlarge, if it is important for you,
shrink, if it is not.


You are what you eat (from the internet). Take good care of it.
